# Ignore all files in the root folder
*
!.gitignore

# Re-include only the docs
!docs/
!docs/**

# Re-include only the AGENTS and HEARTBEAT
!AGENTS.md
!HEARTBEAT.md

# Re-include repo scripts
!scripts/
!scripts/**

# Re-include only the skill folders you want to share
!skills/
!skills/augment-boss-propose/
!skills/augment-boss-propose/**

!skills/augment-boss-execute/
!skills/augment-boss-execute/**

!skills/impl-plan/
!skills/impl-plan/**

!skills/morning-report/
!skills/morning-report/**

!skills/notion-context/
!skills/notion-context/**

!skills/read-excalidraw/
!skills/read-excalidraw/**

# Ignore Python build/runtime artifacts
**/__pycache__/
**/*.pyc
